<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Useless at level one. It lasts 4 sec per level I believe and at level 1 15 manna is kind of a lot for a 4 second snare. Poor little druids learn to hate this spell then find out at higher level how well it works after all. At level 5 it lasts 20 seconds which hopefully is enough time to zone from a mob that would otherwise kill you. At higher levels it will last the duration of the fight, so dont learn to hate it just because its so poor at low level. It will get much better.</font></td></tr></table>
